{"lastModified":1775830731550,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Summer 2026 Operating Area: Balearic Islands, Corsica, French Riviera & Monaco, Italy - North (mainland), Italy - Sardinia, Italy - Sicily, Italy - South (mainland)\n\nWinter 2025/2026 Operating Area: British Virgin Islands, Leeward Islands, US Virgin Islands, Windward Islands\n\nThe Magic of \"NALANI\" – Your Ocean Oasis\n\nDiscover \"NALANI,\" the brand new award-winning Sunreef 80 Eco sailing catamaran where sustainable luxury meets unmatched style. Named after the Hawaiian term for 'serenity under the sky,' NALANI is your ultimate escape on the open sea. Equipped with cutting-edge solar panels, this eco-friendly marvel offers a unique blend of tranquility and sophistication - say goodbye to generator noise, vibrations, and petrol odors while anchored.\n\nBoard NALANI and immerse yourself in a chic, bohemian-inspired haven. Spanning 340 square meters of space, this floating home radiates warmth and elegance with its fine wooden accents, designer furniture, and cozy textiles. Hosting up to 10 guests in four stunning en suite cabins, plus a charming children's bunk room, NALANI ensures everyone has their own slice of paradise. The master cabin boasts a walk-in wardrobe and a private balcony with breathtaking views of the endless horizon.\n\nOutside, NALANI turns heads with a bubbling jacuzzi and an open-air cinema on the flybridge, perfect for movie nights under the stars. With a dedicated crew of four delivering top-notch service, premium cuisine, and expert seamanship, your holiday is in the best hands.\n\nExplore private beaches, dive into crystal-clear waters, or indulge in water sports with an extensive array of water toys, including a top-notch Jetski, two eFoils, two SUPs, water ski, wakeboard, and two Seabobs. NALANI guarantees non-stop fun and excitement for everyone on board.\n\nExperience the future of luxury yachting and make waves with NALANI - where every moment is an unforgettable adventure.","blueprint":{"name":"NALANI","images":["/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfdf1790-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfdec970-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfa96190-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfdb6e10-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfde2d30-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfdddf10-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfdc7f80-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfa78cd0-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfda3590-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfdec971-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfa82911-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfdf65b0-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::eb4ddfa0-f060-11ee-a296-373c493b7d64::assets::bfa82910-3a32-11f0-aaa8-93e5535cd046/{imageVariant}